	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f105007816727925><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj>RE: Melee Skills</span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=140420><span id=Scholar>daneriant</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>80 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Apr 11th 12:59 PM 2003</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.05]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I can truely say that I do not melee EVER!&nbsp;&nbsp;I did up until around level 18.  But our melee skills suck anyways why get melee skills up.  When you get PoP zones, the damage you do through melee is so small.  Might as well nuke!!!<br>Learn what your role is and that will help the group out better.  <br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Daneriant 60 High Priest<br>Danerian&nbsp;&nbsp;56 Outrider<br>Aftermath of Darkness<br>Brell</td></tr>
